            <title><![CDATA[💬👤 #地图帝: 🔗 黄河上中下游是如何划分的？ 白日依山尽，黄河入海流。欲穷千里目，更上一层楼。黄河长约5464千米，居中国第二位，仅次于长江，居世界第...]]></title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1ODM5NjAxMQ==&amp;amp;mid=2247532489&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=797d21541edc59d42e18c58abe95f7af&amp;amp;chksm=fd98c16e3d44c1d7997be41afb4a63dfcf78ad7f6840745d89f09c443a0938319e4b724e1763&amp;amp;scene=0&amp;amp;xtrack=1#rd]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary" style="">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            黄河上中下游是如何划分的？          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">地图弟</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                地图帝              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">地图帝</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">dtdmap</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">左图右史，历史地理不分家。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true"></span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 18px;">白日依山尽，黄河入海流。欲穷千里目，更上一层楼。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">黄河长约5464千米，居中国第二位，仅次于长江，居世界第六。黄河上中下游，是以哪里为分界点的？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048825" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFjDkPJY4nrB2rmCZaETSaictbHXIU1ozvc3EsXsKTNjUmPCsbNjcicZet3DqjANicASVQ0nuljNpiaTiaQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="display: inline;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">黄河源头至内蒙古托克托河口为上游，长约3463千米，约占干流长度的2/3；托克托河口至河南郑州荥阳桃花峪为中游，长约1234千米；桃花峪至黄河口为下游，长约767千米。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>【托克托河口】</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">黄河上游与中游的分界点在托克托河口，即内蒙古呼和浩特托克托县河口古镇，大黑河汇入黄河处，河面海拔约990米。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048828" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFjDkPJY4nrB2rmCZaETSaictgBr0uf5tSLnpbVjqRzPgkEGIl7enJiac1bCpWibToRfDT3ON5soia7WhQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">大黑河由北至南，从大青山上流下，汇入黄河，长约236千米，是黄河在前套平原水量最大的支流。大黑河浑浊暗黑，将大青山腐殖层养分冲刷下来，野沃土肥，宜耕宜牧。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">大黑河由东北向西南冲来，与黄河形成对流格局，故称逆向支流。如今前套平原灌渠纵横，大黑河与黄河交汇处已经被多条人工渠取代，再也见不到大黑河逆流入黄河的壮观景象。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048827" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFjDkPJY4nrB2rmCZaETSaict5XMG8njel3iaderyLpum4WC5DKyjF8cMwNuxryOuic4Em4QhrN6iay6pw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="display: inline;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">托克托县河口古镇，位于黄河北岸，敕勒川（土默川，前套平原）南部。滚滚黄河水，茫茫敕勒川。古代河口就是一个渡口，辽金时期成为货物集散之地，清朝来到鼎盛。河口古镇极盛时期，商家有二百余户，船夫千余人，水道千帆云集。门旗飘动传风色，黄河浪急千帆飞。清朝末年兵连祸结，河口古镇繁华落尽，而又落寂百年！</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">黄河上游河段泥沙汇入仅占总量的8%，水多沙少，是黄河的清水来源。黄河中游河段泥沙汇入占总量的92%，是黄河泥沙的主要来源。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048826" data-ratio="1.5" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFjDkPJY4nrB2rmCZaETSaict0XibxHZd5sO339vLLrGrx170UnOnxWqwWqz2AVPDovNVeZ6gC63CKTQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">黄河中游又分为晋陕峡谷段、汾渭平原段、三门峡至桃花峪河段三部分，其中晋陕峡谷段<span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">支流众多，<span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">泥沙随黄土高原冲入河道，</span></span>泥沙量汇入最大。</span><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>【桃花峪】</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">黄河中游与下游的分界点在桃花峪，即郑州荥阳广武镇桃花峪，河面海拔约96米。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048838" data-ratio="0.7027777777777777" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFjDkPJY4nrB2rmCZaETSaicttv7Dj9pQGAlJ2PicCmZ0KF3rRKmKDyUrSD7Cm64pBrfM8SVbjd3Qfdg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">桃花峪是中国三大阶梯地势第二级、第三级交接点，是山地与平原衔接处。桃花如流瀑，阡陌飘红云。有一种旧的说法，河南洛阳孟津为黄河中下游交接点，新版中学地理教材中，桃花峪才是中下游分界点，我们与时俱进吧。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">桃花峪现在有跨河大桥，南端是郑州荥阳广武镇桃花峪，北端是焦作武陟县圪垱店乡。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048829" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFjDkPJY4nrB2rmCZaETSaictEd5eghmFRAlcznmJ3OWSfpiabJcia2RNibePuysgHpE0V8NjB9fXKPZww/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">在桃花峪以西不远，就是楚汉时期刘邦项羽对峙之地广武涧。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">公元前205年十月至公元前203年九月，刘邦项羽在广武涧对峙，后来双方定下和约，楚、汉两国以鸿沟一水为界。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">广武山在黄河南岸，此山中间断裂，成一深涧，名为广武涧。汉兵在涧西边，筑城驻札。西楚兵在涧东边，亦筑城驻扎。两军各据险阻，相持不下。广武涧分峙两峰，汉王刘邦在西边筑垒，依涧自固，称汉王城。霸王在东边筑垒，与汉相拒，称霸王城。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">黄河从桃花峪到出海口，几乎没有像样的支流，水流平缓，泥沙大量淤积，河床逐渐升高，河面往往高出地面，靠河堤做屏障，是一条“悬河”。</span></p><p><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;'>文：落霞与孤鹜，中国青年政治学院（本科），中央财经大学（硕士），欢迎转载。</span></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzU1ODM5NjAxMQ==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UJLOdsjrZFgmCIpN5LnSBfL46YhOGnNx4LP0utHmFvYohJJAicribSAwraG4EzVKriaszUFicrGF79ib06mu9SqKaxA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="地图帝" data-alias="dtdmap" data-signature="左图右史，历史地理不分家。" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="571312980" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
