            <title><![CDATA[💬👤 #地图帝: 🔗 牧野之战、陈桥兵变在哪？河南新乡 新乡位于河南北部，古称牧野，北依太行、南临黄河，西与山西省、东和山东省接壤。新乡城区南距黄河约...]]></title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1ODM5NjAxMQ==&amp;amp;mid=2247532470&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=ee5249835114551870a237f894b4380e&amp;amp;chksm=fdc82e4412de67206b017123095884271bd275cf33873273dbe515194c3c4f74890afedad3d9&amp;amp;scene=0&amp;amp;xtrack=1#rd]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary" style="">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            牧野之战、陈桥兵变在哪？河南新乡          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">地图弟</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                地图帝              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">地图帝</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">dtdmap</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">左图右史，历史地理不分家。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true"></span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><span style="font-size: 18px;">新乡位于河南北部，古称牧野，北依太行、南临黄河，西与山西省、东和山东省接壤。新乡城区南距黄河约30千米，卫河自西向东穿城而过。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048811" data-ratio="0.9185185185185185" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54QFolcmrpxGDu6UfnfSVmS2vbjOoBAAmdUwGHlia3PeZBQIykMHn3Iu0A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">新乡面积8291约平方千米，人口约617万。新乡有高校（校区）12所，包括河南师范大学、河南科技学院、河南工学院、河南物流职业学院、河南女子职业学院等，在校生20余万，是高校数量较多的非省会城市之一。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048817" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54Q6pZ5ekLRyyG6SfQ7xSRSNLBOX5EhrT5YADybqYchmj92mhEoBfgLsw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">新乡历史悠久、底蕴深厚。仰韶文化、龙山文化留有遗存，牧野之战、官渡之战、陈桥兵变等都发生于此。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>【牧野之战】</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">新乡有牧野区、牧野镇、牧野公园，顾名思义，周灭商的牧野之战，就发生在今新乡。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048809" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54Qm9VWHwDcPPPavLumvSbZNJBib0FyaKkvP3teUHjbHIrpjwNj8eSApQw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">公元前1046年，周国的大军隆隆开动，姬发号召诸侯在孟津集结。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">一月二十六日，周军从镐京出兵。周军的核心是虎贲三千人，有兵车三百乘（兵力三万七千五百），算上其他兵种，总兵力共四万五千。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048816" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54Q3Epxn3PpqVQO38x2icmAicUpmW9rSJGGqgUsLIpInHXic3hQ5r4IAolLQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">二月二十一日，联军在孟津（今河南洛阳孟津）渡过黄河，迅速过商朝的怀（今河南武陟）、宁（今河南获嘉）、共（今河南辉县），一路如水冲沙，似风送雨，未遇抵抗。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">二月二十六日，联军抵达朝歌以南的牧野，遭遇商军，双方摆开阵势。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048815" data-ratio="0.5527777777777778" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54Qydia4ic0pGQgtlUOlsM5RXY8OlkQjEyvVy4MyBkRUMhkLthvLibHfy3sg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">联军长枪千万，寒光闪灼，刀斧影射，威风凛凛，气宇轩昂，人人踊跃，慷慨赴死。征云迷远谷，杀气振原野。联军总兵力约十万，主力是周军的四万五千。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">商军兵力十七万，号称七十万。朝军主力王师，只有两万多人，确实捉襟见肘。不过前来勤王的军队有数万，还有修陵墓和各类工程的奴隶数万。商朝实际还是奴隶社会，后世其他朝代虽然也有奴隶，但比例远不如商朝大。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048812" data-ratio="1.234375" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54QicoYibibAjJ8mcRwNgnRAHbnCD1Hia3djia6wia9Yrtrx0ib51Xb5KK4JSRrQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">二月二十七日，牧野之战打响。诸侯联军气势如虹，战场血流漂杵，死者不计其数，随着猛将恶来阵亡，商军败局已定。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>【陈桥兵变】</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">959年（后周世宗显德六年），柴荣驾崩，七岁的后周恭帝柴宗训即位，契丹与北汉联合南下攻后周。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048810" data-ratio="0.8953703703703704" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54Qsicmrreb2NMn6g7IS4pJNpQzX5lObpAw025hsAJgCglIUwRmjQlQcEQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">960年（周恭帝没来得及改年号）正月，殿前都点检、归德军节度使赵匡胤北上御敌。后周军行至汴京东北陈桥驿（今河南新乡封丘县陈桥镇陈桥村），众将以黄袍加在赵匡胤身上，拥立他为皇帝，赵匡胤“勉为其难”接受，是为宋太祖。随后赵匡胤率军回师开封，在主少国疑的情况下，胁迫后周恭帝禅位。赵匡胤兵不血刃登基，改国号为宋，仍定都汴京（开封）。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">忆昔陈桥兵变时，欺他寡妇与孤儿。谁知三百余年后，寡妇孤儿又被欺。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100048808" data-ratio="1.5" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UJLOdsjrZFh9sPianiceC4pDgjIVJdJ54QxQAgmtu2kmibo0kvRQ40MdoU3zeToXXnfzNAtNN967lVP8F4WibR8TOQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 18px;">三百年后，南宋末代皇帝赵昺年仅七岁，与陆秀夫一同在崖山跳海殉国。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;">陈桥镇陈桥村位于封丘县城南16千米，南距黄河约600米。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;'>文：闫老师，北京大学 硕士 博士，专业 外国语言与外国历史，某高校教师，欢迎转载。</span></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzU1ODM5NjAxMQ==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UJLOdsjrZFgmCIpN5LnSBfL46YhOGnNx4LP0utHmFvYohJJAicribSAwraG4EzVKriaszUFicrGF79ib06mu9SqKaxA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="地图帝" data-alias="dtdmap" data-signature="左图右史，历史地理不分家。" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="323425280" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
